{"tid":797854,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"手機設備股翻生　舜宇曾升逾4%　再成紅底股","createTime":"2018-08-29T00:10:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-29T00:10:07.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9f9cb3095f65977d64663481861a4fce138c9154","tid":797854,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T00:10:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1798198/org/aca2d12e752c421fd3e20e062b238402.jpg/DLntXQnE5yRHQuyQlcefmOJDRWQk31FIaGNzQGhjc0A?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1798198%2Forg%2Faca2d12e752c421fd3e20e062b238402.jpg%2FDLntXQnE5yRHQuyQlcefmOJDRWQk31FIaGNzQGhjc0A%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=ddd2e254&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n手機設備股今早全面復甦，其中大藍等舜宇光學（2382）今早曾高見102.7元，較上日收市價升4.5%，其後升幅略為收窄，最新報101.5元，升3.3%。惟與該公司公布於8月13日公布中期業績前當日，收市價121元相比，仍相差逾16%。<br />\n<br />\n其他手機設備股方面，昨日公布中期業績後股價大跌的丘鈦科技（1478），今早股價出現反彈，最新報5.52元，升2%。該公司管理層於記者會上表示，期望下半年毛利率會有改善。<br />\n<br />\n瑞聲科技（2018）亦錄得0.8%升幅，最新報85.5元，信利國際（0732）升2.4%，最新報1.29元。<br />\n<br />\n撰文：張偉倫<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A/228180/%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E8%A8%AD%E5%82%99%E8%82%A1%E7%BF%BB%E7%94%9F-%E8%88%9C%E5%AE%87%E6%9B%BE%E5%8D%87%E9%80%BE4-%E5%86%8D%E6%88%90%E7%B4%85%E5%BA%95%E8%82%A1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E7%25B6%2593%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E8%25A8%258A%2F228180%2F%25E6%2589%258B%25E6%25A9%259F%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E5%2582%2599%25E8%2582%25A1%25E7%25BF%25BB%25E7%2594%259F-%25E8%2588%259C%25E5%25AE%2587%25E6%259B%25BE%25E5%258D%2587%25E9%2580%25BE4-%25E5%2586%258D%25E6%2588%2590%25E7%25B4%2585%25E5%25BA%2595%25E8%2582%25A1&d=MLQBcG543g5mw53FymU04P%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=fd3af9f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A/228180/%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E8%A8%AD%E5%82%99%E8%82%A1%E7%BF%BB%E7%94%9F-%E8%88%9C%E5%AE%87%E6%9B%BE%E5%8D%87%E9%80%BE4-%E5%86%8D%E6%88%90%E7%B4%85%E5%BA%95%E8%82%A1</a>"}]}